{"tid":484550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有現任仍然掛住前度既你地入一入黎","createTime":"2017-11-30T07:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T14:11:56.000Z","uid":160854,"like":8,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f53df23816f4886d9fbca91794e438081aea01f2","tid":484550,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:33:59.000Z","msg":"如果你地有現任但仍然掛住個ex<br />\n小弟以過來人身份奉勸大家一句<br />\n追番個ex啦！！<br />\n襯時間未長 唔好拖住現任 將對佢既傷害減到最少<br />\n<br />\n小弟同個ex一齊左年幾<br />\n佢唔係我第一個 但係係最深刻個一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢真係陪我經歷左好多<br />\n我最冇錢既時候佢不離不棄 食飯自動aa<br />\n聖誕節叫我唔好送禮物等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢除左發脾氣之外真係好完美<br />\n最後分手係佢提出 我有挽留但佢唔受 <br />\n之後我極速搵左個新歡黎忘記佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我ex之後搵番我 佢好多厹追但佢話佢未放低我所以冇開始<br />\n但呢個時候我已經洗濕左個頭搵左現任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但其實我耐唔耐都會好掛住個ex<br />\n最後比我朋友屌醒左 我跟本一直當現任水泡 唔習慣冇左ex個種空虛 唔習慣由兩個人變成一個人生活<br />\n於是襯同現任感情未深 我同佢講左分手 追番個ex<br />\n最後同現任仲做得番朋友 因為大家未發展到好認真 大家都唔太傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成功追番個ex 同ex個種幸褔其實真係冇人取替到<br />\n一齊番之後大家都好珍惜大家 佢都改左好多脾氣<br />\n所以各位巴打 勇敢啲去追你心目中個個人啦<br />\n問下自己 而家既你真係幸福咩？"},{"pid":"e4108930660323a86c60c08eb18138523219e38c","tid":484550,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:57:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a3579dbf26dac88b9bddb5b4dce6d2cd806b794d","tid":484550,"uid":56961,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:00:59.000Z","msg":"賤人"},{"pid":"924f58cc88e508d850cd8fb07113613358a692ed","tid":484550,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賤人</blockquote><br />\n唔錯都錯左 只可以補救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be0672dbd42549c168f31bbeaaf1c989316e182","tid":484550,"uid":160668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:22:56.000Z","msg":"做你水泡個個真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2192dcdb17e3d4ac409edaf478d62d34fc436078","tid":484550,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做你水泡個個真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好彩既係一齊左冇耐，佢對我感情都唔深，事後我都有同佢道歉，佢話可以做番朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2354dfb0ccee0661f8a204aa68dc9db7e8cd556f","tid":484550,"uid":160668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"係咪兩個都扑過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78a97843d1380d37b76890469c2a783704c3120","tid":484550,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪兩個都扑過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEx有 現任冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67da71494f7dc83db49aacc71454197d6737aa2","tid":484550,"uid":160668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"蝕左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d229fa85abb78574cb7d22d845512176980f8b1","tid":484550,"uid":8158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"分左手冇耐 希望佢都會見到呢個post 最後會同翻我一齊 佢真係我最深刻既一個 經歷得太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  兜兜轉轉 我好掛住你啊 番黎啦 我會改過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04002ef59dae2fe0a98ab392c6b7149df0799ea5","tid":484550,"uid":32684,