 />\n祝你地最後可以成功一齊番！"},{"pid":"996a8eefcf182b3798187fa812ed764273e7fa7b","tid":484550,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:09:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外想問下樓豬  大約幾耐先開始有咁嘅諗法？</blockquote><br />\n同ex散左2個幾月 同現任一齊左個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b200ba5e0331a7ae8b31c42de7b81cd80bab0900","tid":484550,"uid":22359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>另外想問下樓豬  大約幾耐先開始有咁嘅諗法？</blockquote><br />\n同ex散左2個幾月 同現任一齊左個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係加加埋埋 同ex散左 4個幾月 先再一齊返？"},{"pid":"b89fd192f0adb032f30e42d72fc8c15a9a9215d7","tid":484550,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>另外想問下樓豬  大約幾耐先開始有咁嘅諗法？</blockquote><br />\n同ex散左2個幾月 同現任一齊左個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係加加埋埋 同ex散左 4個幾月 先再一齊返？</blockquote><br />\n同ex total散左2個幾月"},{"pid":"fb43bd1e6a0982d667a38da14c3483a295655b3f","tid":484550,"uid":160854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T11:15:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>另外想問下樓豬  大約幾耐先開始有咁嘅諗法？</blockquote><br />\n同ex散左2個幾月 同現任一齊左個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係加加埋埋 同ex散左 4個幾月 先再一齊返？</blockquote><br />\n有需要可pm我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9637dc0a157022016637739e822f5eac7252ad53","tid":484550,"uid":22359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>另外想問下樓豬  大約幾耐先開始有咁嘅諗法？</blockquote><br />\n同ex散左2個幾月 同現任一齊左個幾月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係加加埋埋 同ex散左 4個幾月 先再一齊返？</blockquote><br />\n有需要可pm我<img src=\"/assets/fac